Nice, spacious apartment with good location in Charlottenlund. Here you have easy access to Ordrup station, shopping, schools, day care centers and sports activities. In addition, there is a short distance to scenic areas such as Skovshoved Harbour, Charlottenlund Strandpark (beach/park), Dyrehaven (forest) and Bellevue (beach). Inside you are greeted by an inviting entrance hall with good storage space, a newer kitchen with nice, white elements and a newer bathroom. In addition, a spacious living room with access to a west-facing balcony and two bedrooms with wardrobes. All in all a lovely apartment. Private parking space and cellar is included.
